doc.after: Lesotho s geographic location makes it extremely vulnerable to political and economic developments in South Africa It is a member of many regional economic organizations including the Southern African Development Community SADC 16 and the Southern African Customs Union SACU 17 It is also active in the United Nations UN the African Union the Non Aligned Movement the Commonwealth and many other international organizations citation needed
